332
00:20:39,539 --> 00:20:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] u većoj skupini ljudi,

333
00:20:43,099 --> 00:20:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] znaš, tako kad se mi muški skupimo i sad,

334
00:20:48,380 --> 00:20:54,059
[SPEAKER_00] to je isto neki oblik, manji minijaturni oblik javnog nastupa.

335
00:20:55,059 --> 00:20:56,839
[SPEAKER_00] Na sedmeru, osmeru muških se skupi,

336
00:20:56,839 --> 00:21:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] sjedimo svi za stolom, neka je večera, neko je druženje

337
00:21:00,059 --> 00:21:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] i sad ti se trebaš, recimo, ti želiš neku priču ispričati,

338
00:21:03,980 --> 00:21:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] ti želiš nešto na glas reći što ću ovih drugih šest, sedam čuti.

339
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nekad i u tim odnosima mi onako dosta je to subtilno,

340
00:21:14,519 --> 00:21:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] možda i intuitivno i podsvjesno.

341
00:21:17,420 --> 00:21:23,640
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, svi mi neke granice pokušavamo ne prijeći,

342
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:27,799
[SPEAKER_00] netko misli da može možda preći malo više u komunikaciji,

343
00:21:27,799 --> 00:21:30,519
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda tu budu i tih muških fora, znaš,

344
00:21:30,519 --> 00:21:33,839
[SPEAKER_00] pa nekoga malo i uvrijediš, pa ga malo isprovociraš ovako, onako.

345
00:21:33,839 --> 00:21:38,839
[SPEAKER_00] Da li misliš da ti je to, recimo, ta vještina hrvanja

346
00:21:38,839 --> 00:21:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] i to možda samo opuzdanje, koji si dobio kroz to,

347
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] da ti je dalo malo više slobode da se bolje izraziš,

348
00:21:46,420 --> 00:21:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] recimo da se bolje postaviš, zauzmeš za sebe

349
00:21:49,859 --> 00:21:51,819
[SPEAKER_00] u odnosu sa drugim ljudima?

350
00:21:53,420 --> 00:21:56,180
[SPEAKER_01] Nedvojbeno, da. Si me podsjetio zapravo

351
00:21:56,180 --> 00:22:02,759
[SPEAKER_01] sa bavljanjem karatea, dakle, prije početka hrvanja.

352
00:22:02,759 --> 00:22:06,240
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bio dječak koji je bio onako,

353
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:09,279
[SPEAKER_01] koju kilicu viška sam imao.

354
00:22:09,279 --> 00:22:12,579
[SPEAKER_01] A znam i pamtim da u petom razlihu,

355
00:22:12,579 --> 00:22:16,339
[SPEAKER_01] neki su me zvali, to su bile zlonamene u toj dobi vršnjaka,

356
00:22:16,420 --> 00:22:19,180
[SPEAKER_01] ono debeli. Daleko od toga da sam ja bio debel ono.

357
00:22:19,180 --> 00:22:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ali bilo je to onako, pa nisam debel i to.

358
00:22:21,039 --> 00:22:23,940
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerojatno iz toga se opet vuče ono da sam ja htio imati mišiće.

359
00:22:23,940 --> 00:22:29,759
[SPEAKER_01] I ko što ti je rekao, prve pobjede, pa porast, pa pobjede.

360
00:22:29,759 --> 00:22:31,279
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ti samo bildaš samopouzdanje.

361
00:22:31,279 --> 00:22:35,200
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo u Hrvanju i svakim treningom to samopouzdanje je raslo.

362
00:22:35,940 --> 00:22:39,759
[SPEAKER_01] Onda u Hrvanju imaš te neke, bar smo imali u klubu,

363
00:22:39,759 --> 00:22:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] idole koji su desetak godina stariji od tebe,

364
00:22:43,539 --> 00:22:44,900
[SPEAKER_01] što je velika razlika tada.

365
00:22:44,900 --> 00:22:51,740
[SPEAKER_01] Pa onda gledaš njihove gegove i oni su ti tvoji neki, da, idoli.

366
00:22:51,740 --> 00:22:55,339
[SPEAKER_01] Ti želiš biti ja, ko on, ali gledaj ko on dobro je komunicira,

367
00:22:55,339 --> 00:22:57,039
[SPEAKER_01] kak se on zeza, kak su to.

368
00:22:57,039 --> 00:23:01,900
[SPEAKER_01] I zapravo smo mi, ono, ta hrvačka obitelj,

369
00:23:01,900 --> 00:23:03,799
[SPEAKER_01] kroz generacije i ovi stariji i mlaji,

370
00:23:04,380 --> 00:23:06,599
[SPEAKER_01] tako smo mi, kad smo dobili ove klince mlađe,

371
00:23:06,599 --> 00:23:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] na neki način kužiš da si mu idol

372
00:23:09,420 --> 00:23:14,400
[SPEAKER_01] i ne samo tijelesno samopouzdanje,

373
00:23:14,400 --> 00:23:16,740
[SPEAKER_01] nego samopouzdanje na svim razlijenom na neki način

374
00:23:16,740 --> 00:23:23,240
[SPEAKER_01] dobivaš i koje ti je izuzetno dobro došlo u životu.

375
00:23:23,240 --> 00:23:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Spomenio si u jednom trenutku,

376
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] ajde, nastavit ćemo kroz tvoju priču dalje.

377
00:23:32,819 --> 00:23:35,519
[SPEAKER_00] znači, hrvanje u Petrinji,

378
00:23:35,519 --> 00:23:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] nekako rano u djetinstvo,

379
00:23:37,539 --> 00:23:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] karate,

380
00:23:39,039 --> 00:23:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda si u jednom trenutku spomenio da si kroz,

381
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako si bio rekao,

382
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:46,859
[SPEAKER_00] kroz molitvu,

383
00:23:46,859 --> 00:23:51,299
[SPEAKER_00] ili spomenio si možda nešto

384
00:23:51,299 --> 00:23:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] i u drugačijem kontekstu,

385
00:23:54,019 --> 00:23:56,059
[SPEAKER_00] osim molitve,

386
00:23:56,059 --> 00:23:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] da si počeo grebati to nešto,

387
00:23:58,680 --> 00:24:00,200
[SPEAKER_00] metafizičko nešto, nešto.

388
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ču sad to nazvat duhovno ili ću nazvat to psihološki ili ću nazvat nešto,

389
00:24:07,599 --> 00:24:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] uglavnom nešto metafizičko.

390
00:24:09,460 --> 00:24:16,160
[SPEAKER_00] Osim tog tijelesnog, recimo, rada i razvoja,

391
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:20,180
[SPEAKER_00] koje je naravno povezano sa tim psihološkim dijelom ili nekim metafizičkim dijelom,

392
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:27,839
[SPEAKER_00] kako izgleda taj dio djetinstva ili onda kasnije možda adolescencije

393
00:24:27,839 --> 00:24:30,339
[SPEAKER_00] u tom nekom tvom razvoju

394
00:24:30,339 --> 00:24:33,640
[SPEAKER_00] ili prvom nekakom shvaćanju sebe tko sam ja,

395
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,140
[SPEAKER_00] ono i tako neke stvari.

396
00:24:35,140 --> 00:24:39,339
[SPEAKER_00] Na šta si nailazio da ti je nekako zagoli celo maštu,

397
00:24:39,339 --> 00:24:42,220
[SPEAKER_00] pa si nastavio koristiti dalje u životu možda?

398
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:47,180
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to kad sam, ok, prvi neki kontakt sa tim,

399
00:24:47,180 --> 00:24:49,279
[SPEAKER_01] možda mislim, neopipljivo sam termini.

400
00:24:49,279 --> 00:24:49,920
[SPEAKER_01] Neopipljivo, da.

401
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:56,559
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ok, išto se na vjeronauku, to su te ratne godine,

402
00:24:56,559 --> 00:25:00,680
[SPEAKER_01] pa ta prva priča, ok, ali, to se živo svićam,

403
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] baš onak neugodno to bilo stanje za vrijeme rata

404
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:04,900
[SPEAKER_01] i sad smo mi tamo i baka, dida i mama, tate.

405
00:25:04,900 --> 00:25:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam nešto to, ok, ajmo to nazvat molitva, definitivno,

406
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:13,660
[SPEAKER_01] ali, koliko se znam, zatvorene su oči bile

407
00:25:13,660 --> 00:25:16,859
[SPEAKER_01] i sad ja sam djete koji ne znam baš o kvantne fizici ništa,

408
00:25:16,859 --> 00:25:19,660
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam ni sada, ali znam, ipak sam čitao neke knjige,

409
00:25:19,660 --> 00:25:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] ali ono, nikako duboko neka vjera,

410
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:26,200
[SPEAKER_01] da budu mama, tata, dobro, baka, di dobro,

411
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:28,720
[SPEAKER_01] da sve nek idem smjerom dobrim

412
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:33,420
[SPEAKER_01] i definitivno se to onda realiziralo u životu,

413
00:25:33,420 --> 00:25:35,099
[SPEAKER_01] da je sve bilo, eto, i dobro.

414
00:25:35,099 --> 00:25:40,140
[SPEAKER_01] Znam da sam i prije svakog izlaska u borbu,

415
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] u nekoj intimi tamo iza tribine

416
00:25:42,980 --> 00:25:48,039
[SPEAKER_01] bi se ja prekrižio i išao u borbu.

417
00:25:48,039 --> 00:25:50,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mogu sad baš sjetiti točno

418
00:25:50,420 --> 00:25:54,240
[SPEAKER_01] da li je to bilo da, u smislu,

419
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:56,700
[SPEAKER_01] da dam sve od sebe, možda i da pobjedim,

420
00:25:56,700 --> 00:25:59,720
[SPEAKER_01] ili da ostanem čitav i zdrav,

421
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:02,440
[SPEAKER_01] ok, u Hrvanju nisu toliko česte ozvjede,

422
00:26:02,839 --> 00:26:05,099
[SPEAKER_01] ali znaju biti, ja sam imao konkretnu frakturu,

423
00:26:05,099 --> 00:26:07,019
[SPEAKER_01] nadlaktice, baš u borbi.

424
00:26:07,019 --> 00:26:10,400
[SPEAKER_01] A znam da sam odlazio tam iz tribine,

425
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] dakle nešto moje što nisem u potrebu javno,

426
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:16,200
[SPEAKER_01] pa ti tamo nešto, da publika gleda,

427
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,779
[SPEAKER_01] nego da niko ne vidi to je moje

428
00:26:17,779 --> 00:26:23,180
[SPEAKER_01] i kažem, ja to nisam tad znao opisati,

429
00:26:23,180 --> 00:26:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] ali moglo bi se zvati molitva,

430
00:26:26,380 --> 00:26:30,799
[SPEAKER_01] kratka neka, doticanje s tim nečim uzvišenim,

431
00:26:30,799 --> 00:26:33,599
[SPEAKER_01] ali kad kažem molitva,

432
00:26:33,599 --> 00:26:36,200
[SPEAKER_01] nije samo da se tiče ono sad hršćanstva,

433
00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:38,359
[SPEAKER_01] crkve, neg nešto ono,

434
00:26:38,359 --> 00:26:46,200
[SPEAKER_01] i sad je to meni teško opisati što točno,

435
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:48,680
[SPEAKER_01] definitivno vjerujem u to nešto što je

436
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:52,119
[SPEAKER_01] nas stvorilo, ta neka energija

437
00:26:52,119 --> 00:26:56,839
[SPEAKER_01] i to je jednako važno kultivirat,

438
00:26:56,839 --> 00:26:59,799
[SPEAKER_01] što je važno, ne jednako,

439
00:26:59,799 --> 00:27:00,980
[SPEAKER_01] nego možda i važnije,

440
00:27:00,980 --> 00:27:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] to je možda u temelju,

441
00:27:02,380 --> 00:27:03,819
[SPEAKER_01] nego samo tijelo.

442
00:27:03,819 --> 00:27:06,019
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je originalna izreka

443
00:27:06,019 --> 00:27:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] ide u zdravom duhu, u zdravo tijelo,

444
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:11,359
[SPEAKER_01] a ne u zdravom tijelu, u zdravom duhu.

445
00:27:11,359 --> 00:27:12,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ili mislim da...

446
00:27:12,319 --> 00:27:15,440
[SPEAKER_01] Može biti obron, to je povezano,

447
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:17,299
[SPEAKER_01] ali mislim da je originalna u zdravom duhu,

448
00:27:17,299 --> 00:27:17,980
[SPEAKER_01] u zdravom tijelu.

449
00:27:17,980 --> 00:27:20,180
[SPEAKER_01] Jednom periodu života,

450
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:23,079
[SPEAKER_01] kao da sam se udaljio

451
00:27:23,079 --> 00:27:25,440
[SPEAKER_01] od to taj kad sam uzograo

452
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:27,539
[SPEAKER_01] u taj show, biznis i to sve.

453
00:27:27,539 --> 00:27:28,680
[SPEAKER_01] Kao da sam se,

454
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:30,839
[SPEAKER_01] kao da sam napravio neki odmak,

455
00:27:30,839 --> 00:27:31,819
[SPEAKER_01] nesvjesno,

456
00:27:31,819 --> 00:27:34,640
[SPEAKER_01] od tog neopipljivog i

457
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:38,359
[SPEAKER_01] da sam živo taj neki površni,

458
00:27:38,359 --> 00:27:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] džir na valu možda,

459
00:27:40,579 --> 00:27:41,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je u meni bilo,

460
00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:43,220
[SPEAKER_01] to je iskustvo djeteta koje imalo to

461
00:27:43,220 --> 00:27:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] do se sada neopipljivim.

462
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] A onda te život opet vrati

463
00:27:46,579 --> 00:27:47,339
[SPEAKER_01] i onda opet,

464
00:27:47,339 --> 00:27:48,799
[SPEAKER_01] znam da sam bio u potrazi

465
00:27:48,799 --> 00:27:50,640
[SPEAKER_01] prije nekih deset godina, nešto više,

466
00:27:51,200 --> 00:27:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] kako svako jutro radim tu svoju

467
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:54,079
[SPEAKER_01] jutarnju tijelovježbu,

468
00:27:54,079 --> 00:27:56,900
[SPEAKER_01] tražio sam da tako

469
00:27:56,900 --> 00:27:58,299
[SPEAKER_01] kao što imam jutarnju tijelovježbu,

470
00:27:58,299 --> 00:27:59,119
[SPEAKER_01] tražio sam za

471
00:27:59,119 --> 00:28:01,500
[SPEAKER_01] takozvane duhovnih deset sklekova.

472
00:28:01,500 --> 00:28:02,359
[SPEAKER_01] Kako mogu,

473
00:28:02,359 --> 00:28:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] nerealno da sad ja sada tipa

474
00:28:04,460 --> 00:28:05,400
[SPEAKER_01] svaki dan meditiram.

475
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:06,359
[SPEAKER_01] Nije održivo,

476
00:28:06,359 --> 00:28:07,220
[SPEAKER_01] neću svaki dan,

477
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:07,680
[SPEAKER_01] sigurno ne.

478
00:28:07,680 --> 00:28:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] Nekako nešto.

479
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:10,619
[SPEAKER_01] I onda sam ti napravio

480
00:28:10,619 --> 00:28:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] neku sinergiju,

481
00:28:12,500 --> 00:28:14,019
[SPEAKER_01] mišung

482
00:28:14,019 --> 00:28:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] i od nekoliko knjiga

483
00:28:16,079 --> 00:28:17,920
[SPEAKER_01] svoju neku derivaciju

484
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:19,119
[SPEAKER_01] koja meni odgovara

485
00:28:19,119 --> 00:28:20,220
[SPEAKER_01] duše ja radim na večer.

486
00:28:20,220 --> 00:28:22,460
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ti ja,

487
00:28:22,460 --> 00:28:22,839
[SPEAKER_01] eto,

488
00:28:22,839 --> 00:28:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] a opet,

489
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:25,019
[SPEAKER_01] roditelji

490
00:28:25,019 --> 00:28:26,720
[SPEAKER_01] nisu imali,

491
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je dokaz da eto,

492
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:30,400
[SPEAKER_01] znam meni i tata reći,

493
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,680
[SPEAKER_01] pa ti Mario,

494
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:32,680
[SPEAKER_01] ko da nisi tu,

495
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] kad ja nešto počnem ovoga,

496
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:36,099
[SPEAKER_01] svoje,

497
00:28:36,099 --> 00:28:37,299
[SPEAKER_01] pa ti ko da nisi tu,

498
00:28:37,299 --> 00:28:38,359
[SPEAKER_01] od nas,

499
00:28:38,359 --> 00:28:39,380
[SPEAKER_01] ko da nisi tu odrasto.

500
00:28:39,380 --> 00:28:40,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ali eto,

501
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,779
[SPEAKER_01] od njih sa roditelja

502
00:28:41,779 --> 00:28:42,720
[SPEAKER_01] i dijete dođe,

503
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:43,740
[SPEAKER_01] što je rekao ja,

504
00:28:43,740 --> 00:28:45,819
[SPEAKER_01] mi ne dolazimo

505
00:28:45,819 --> 00:28:47,779
[SPEAKER_01] od naših roditelja,

506
00:28:47,779 --> 00:28:49,319
[SPEAKER_01] nego kroz njih.

507
00:28:49,319 --> 00:28:51,259
[SPEAKER_01] Nikakve veze s sportom,

508
00:28:51,259 --> 00:28:51,900
[SPEAKER_01] nikakve tu,

509
00:28:51,900 --> 00:28:52,660
[SPEAKER_01] a ja zabriju,

510
00:28:52,660 --> 00:28:53,279
[SPEAKER_01] ni sestra,

511
00:28:53,279 --> 00:28:53,819
[SPEAKER_01] starija od mene,

512
00:28:53,819 --> 00:28:54,259
[SPEAKER_01] četiri godine,

513
00:28:54,259 --> 00:28:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] nema veze,

514
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] nije ona bila u sportu.

515
00:28:56,420 --> 00:28:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da eto,

516
00:28:58,559 --> 00:28:59,799
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam zahvalan na tome

517
00:28:59,799 --> 00:29:00,619
[SPEAKER_01] što, eto,

518
00:29:00,619 --> 00:29:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] koračan tim putem,

519
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:05,259
[SPEAKER_01] zdravlja na svim razinama.

520
00:29:05,259 --> 00:29:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] Kako izgleda jedna,

521
00:29:08,619 --> 00:29:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] pretpostavljiv sam kroz ovo,

522
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:11,660
[SPEAKER_00] sve što si rekao,

523
